<header class="row p-3 border-bottom border-5">
  <h1 class="col-10">
    <a href="/">
      Med Planner
    </a>
  </h1>
  <nav class="col-2">
      <a class="btn" href="/signup">
        Sign Up
      </a>
      <a class="btn" href="/signin">
        Caregiver
      </a>
  </nav>
</header>


<section class="p-7">
  <p class="fs-3 text-dark">
    Welcome to the med planner. Your one stop for setting up what you need with the right physicians. Here you can find your primary
        physician and specialist. You can make, change, or cancel your appointments. You can also use out appointment tracker to remind you
        of up coming appointments. Use the form below to sign up and just see how easy it all is.
  </p>
</section>
<div class="col-3 form">
<form class="signIn-patient round p-4">
  <div class="row mb-1">
    <h3>
      Patient Sign In
    </h3>
    <div class="col-auto">
      <input
        type="email"
        class="form-control round"
        id="email-signIn"
        placeholder="Email Address"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row mb-1">
    <div class="col-auto">
      <input
        type="password"
        class="form-control round"
        id="password-signIn"
        placeholder="Password"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <button type="submit" class="btn sign-in">
    Sign in
  </button>
</form>
</div>

<script src="/js/login.js"></script>